.TP 
\fB\-\-debug\-lua\fP
启用一些Lua调试机制
.TP 
\fB\-e[\fP\fIfile\fP\fB],\ \-\-editor[\fP\fI=file\fP\fB]\fP
start the in\-game map editor directly. If \fIfile\fP is specified, equivalent
