will be preprocessed before the specified resources.  Example: \fB\-p
~/wesnoth/data/campaigns/tutorial ~/result.\fP For details regarding the
preprocessor visit:
https://wiki.wesnoth.org/PreprocessorRef#Command\-line_preprocessor.
